Project Title
Student Attendance Tracker Web Application

Objective

Build a web application that allows institutions to manage students and track daily attendance, with role-based access for Admin and Teacher and reporting features.

Functional Requirements
User Roles

Role

Permissions

Admin

Manage teachers & students, view all reports

Teacher

Mark attendance & view attendance for their assigned students only

Modules & Features
Authentication

Login & Logout
Password encryption
Session/token-based authentication
Admin Panel

Add / Edit / Delete Teachers (CRUD)
Add / Edit / Delete Students (CRUD)
Assign students to teachers
Dashboard with key numbers (optional)
Teacher Panel

View assigned students
Mark attendance (Present / Absent)
Date-wise attendance marking
Attendance Management

Prevent duplicate attendance for the same day
Allow modifying attendance for previous days (optional)
Reporting

View student-wise attendance report
View month-wise summary (present %, absent %)
Export report (CSV / PDF – optional)
